description:
One owner. Dealer serviced.  Top of the line trim level. Eco Diesel Turbo Diesel V6 engine.  Eco Mode. 8 speed ZF transmission. 4x4. Up to 1,300 kilometer driving range. Best in class fuel economy at 7.0 - 10.4L per 100 kms hwy-city. 8.4 - 9.9 combined. Depending on driving conditions and weather, fuel economy can be improved. 420 lb-ft of torque at a very low 2,000 rpm. 7,200 pound towing capacity

Alcantara suede pillars and headliner.Panoramic sunroof with power auto shade. Front heated and cooled leather seats. Also has heated rear seats. Heated steering wheel with paddle shifters. 8.4” touchscreen. 3D Navigation. Comfort controls, XM satellite radio, etc. Harman/Kardon 825 watt 19 speaker sound system. Back up camera with front and rear proximity sensors. UConnect infotainment system offers Bluetooth handsfree and music streaming. Full air ride suspension. Quadra-Lift air suspension that can raise or lower the Jeep to five different heights. Quadra-Drive II 4 wheel drive system. Electronic-slip differential and a two-speed transfer case. Selec-Terrain with 5 different surface driving modes. Auto, snow, sport, sand/mud, and rock. Blind spot monitoring with rear cross path detection. Adaptive cruise control. Adaptive headlights. LED daytime running lights. Forward collision warning. Rain sensing wipers along with rain brake support help dry the rotors to ensure shortest stopping distance when it’s raining. New Toyo winter tires. New windshield and front windshield wipers. Rear wiper also replaced.
